Angular Applications.

    We Can Create Two Types Of Angular Applications.

1.Static Angular Application.

2.Dynamic Angular Application.


Static Angular Application.

    If View Not Interacting With Controller for Dynamic Data , such type

    angular application called as Static Angular Application.

Dynamic Angular Application.

    - If View Interacting with the Controller for Dynamic Data ,

      such type of Application called as Dynamic Angular Application.

Steps to Create the Static Angular Application.

Step 1.

    Download the Angular Framework by using bower.

-------------------
Lecture@5
    bower.json
    .bowerrc.json
--------------------


Step 2.

    Create the View.

index.html
-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app>
    <input type="number" ng-model="model_one">
    <br><br>
    <input type="number" ng-model="model_two">
    <br><br>
    <h1 style="color:red" ng-bind="model_one+model_two"></h1>
    <script src = "bower_components/angular/angular.min.js"></script>
</html>



